package drivers

import (
    "context"
    "testing"
    "github.com/stretchr/testify/assert"
    "os"
)

func TestYouTubeAdapter_GetSearching(t *testing.T) {
    os.Setenv("YOUTUBE_API_KEY", "test_api_key")
    ytAdapter, err := NewYouTubeAdapter()
    assert.NoError(t, err)
    assert.NotNil(t, ytAdapter)

    data, err := ytAdapter.GetSearching(context.Background(), "test query")
    assert.NoError(t, err)
    assert.NotNil(t, data)
}
